::Magmatron::

    Magmatron sat in the dark of his room. It was furnished with all the 
things he needed, his weapons and some memories from Cybertron. He was making 
plans for the Maximals, maybe he could send CyberShark to infiltrate the 
base. 
    Hmmmm...I think that might work, just gonna be kinda painful for 
CyberShark. Magmatron thought to himself. Yes, it will be a sorry day for the 
Maximals when CyberShark enters the base.
